  "pageTitle": "数字化回收流程参考案例",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-ai\"> <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">智能回收案例</p> <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">数字化回收流程参考案例</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">资源回收中心参考资料，结合了分选模块、称重、报告和远程操作可视化。</p></section> <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"smart-recovery-center\" aria-labelledby=\"smart-recovery-center-timeline-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">系统流程</p> <h2 id=\"smart-recovery-center-timeline-title\">案例范围将接收、分选、称重与报告整合为一套流程</h2> <p>案例按项目评估流程排序：背景、合作单位、限制、解决方案以及前后对比。</p></div> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例流程时间线\"> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">项目背景</p> <h3>混合物料运营场景</h3> <p>该中心结合了接收、物料分拣、分类、称重、存储和出库物流，涵盖混合可回收和市政废弃物流。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>工作流程区域</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">6 区域</strong><span>从接收到出库</span></dd></div> <div><dt>物料范围</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 类物料流</strong><span>可回收物与市政废弃物</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作单位</p> <h3>城市级服务运营</h3> <p>合作单位需要对进料物料、分选产出、每日运行状态及管理评估报告的更好可视性。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>管理层</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 个驾驶舱</strong><span>中央操作显示</span></dd></div> <div><dt>评审模式</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">每日</strong><span>输出与状态报告</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">实际限制</p> <h3>物料流与数据流同步</h3> <p>该项目必须连接分选模块、称重点、驾驶舱显示、存储区和远程管理，同时不将操作与报告分离。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>数据点</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">3 组</strong><span>输入 / 输出 / 状态</span></dd></div> <div><dt>远程需求</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 个接口</strong><span>管理可视性</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解决方案</p> <h3>分选与数字驾驶舱集成范围</h3> <p>参考包涵盖分选模块、智能称重点、驾驶舱显示、远程管理界面，以及报告支持的吞吐量和类别。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>系统模块</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 个模块</strong><span>分类/称重/报告/管理</span></dd></div> <div><dt>输出视图</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 仪表盘</strong><span>驾驶舱摘要</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前后对比</p> <h3>可视化运营记录</h3> <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\"> <div><span>之前</span><strong>分离的物料流与报告</strong><p>管理者对接收、分类和存储日常连接的了解有限。</p></div> <div><span>之后</span><strong>从接收到报告的可见路径</strong><p>参考视频和驾驶舱截图展示了物料路线、分选产出和报告工作流程。</p></div></div> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>记录材料</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 类资料</strong><span>视频和驾驶舱截图</span></dd></div></dl></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section ai-rfq-section\" aria-label=\"案例操作\"> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求参考包</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回参考案例</a></div></section></main>"
